==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: wù yĭ shàn xiăo ér bù wéi
===Etymology===
a quote from the ''[[wikipedia:Romance of the Three Kingdoms|Romance of the Three Kingdoms]]''
===Proverb===
'''[[勿]][[以]][[善]][[小]][[而]][[不]][[为]]'''
# Do not fail to commit an act of kindness just because it is small in scale.
===Alternate forms===
[[勿以善小而不為]] ([[Traditional Chinese]])

===Related terms===
*[[勿以恶小而为之]]

